WEBVTT

00:00:07.454 --> 00:00:11.246
How can you get what you want
using just your words?

00:00:11.288 --> 00:00:14.871
Aristotle set out to answer exactly
that question over 2,000 years ago

00:00:14.913 --> 00:00:17.204
with the “Treatise on Rhetoric”.

00:00:18.163 --> 00:00:19.954
Rhetoric, according to Aristotle,

00:00:19.996 --> 00:00:23.121
is the art of seeing
the available means of persuasion.

00:00:23.163 --> 00:00:26.954
And today, we apply it
to any form of communication.

00:00:27.246 --> 00:00:30.371
Aristotle focused on oration though,